Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.17,0:00:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\N Just Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.07,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.61,0:00:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.72,0:00:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.93,0:00:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.73,0:00:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.01,0:01:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.45,0:01:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.12,0:01:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.46,0:01:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開地球的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.37,0:01:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙殖民衛星的生活裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.91,0:01:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉正義及和平為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.01,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以壓倒性的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓制著各個殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.86,0:01:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰名稱[流星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.56,0:01:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和聯合反目的部份衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.10,0:01:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定把偽裝為流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.03,0:01:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.64,0:02:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早已被聯合總部發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的報告我聽過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望德利安外務次官你退席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不清醒一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正危險的人是你們自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.05,0:02:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!你指誰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.39,0:02:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快點來殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第五話\N[莉莉娜的秘密]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德利安外務次官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒適的旅程很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.91,0:03:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊聊天沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.28,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和SMS的人沒話題可說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很不近人情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上層叫我監視你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當我是敵人我也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.90,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從外面看地球是多美麗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再也沒機會再看了，德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳突然嘆氣做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民衛星在那麼美麗的星海裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何它們不發光?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，現在沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為莉莉娜小姐去了衛星那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們會比平時明亮數倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，北太平洋OZ補給基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德利安先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.91,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球經濟不景看來是謠傳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有經費發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,專屬你們的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種謠傳還無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合裡流傳的謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻不能一笑置之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謠傳我們進攻地球那件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.96,0:05:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們那樣做根本不容我們解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來訪的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.50,0:05:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是查明那是否是謠傳和內部真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望那是謠傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球的人為何會認為?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.03,0:05:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在這麼和平真誠衛星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會發起戰爭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，蕾蒂小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.51,0:05:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是地球方面的外交人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.18,0:06:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能容許妳在場參加會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但可以告訴我會議結果嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那麼我失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10分鍾後，那就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是開始才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去買點東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上準備護衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡比地球安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個人的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是不講理的話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼流星作戰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼新型機動戰士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們毫不知情!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德利安先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合為何不信任我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有10秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.86,0:07:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，這是妳遺失的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.28,0:07:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉住那女孩，反抗就殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!你在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德利安他沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人全部死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是甚麼人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.31,0:08:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，快帶走德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道   你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡做甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有班人帶著德利安\N和女孩逃亡中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請在停車場截著他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.56,0:08:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要妳跟我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那麼年輕不想死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事怎樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們想怎樣處置我爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在妳要服從我們的指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，妳會冷靜一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快送我爸爸去醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.53,0:09:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這樣會死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫院很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.77,0:09:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.93,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他們已先派人去了那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的組織有優秀的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.07,0:09:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們究竟是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我講，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!爸爸，你別說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.29,0:09:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是…妳真正的爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的真名是…\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是以前提倡和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匹斯克拉福特王族的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…代代侍奉那國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元老院的一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…她被聯合亡國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃出來的我把妳當為女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是假的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.32,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心OZ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…爸爸!你不要死!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藥看來有效了，她睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士的修理完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝，麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.86,0:10:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要有錢收就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好主顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.57,0:10:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算趕得上下一個任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會留你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.59,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，至少告訴我你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫卡特爾‧拉巴伯‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想叫的就叫我特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.13,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，特洛瓦，後會有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣讓他走沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道我們的\N根據地在這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.78,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那麼多嘴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他來進攻…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我歡迎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就能再次和他見面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要沉悶監視兩小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各部份正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在前往目標地點完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了，奧圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我，這班技師很優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會把它完成至完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部二十多年前設計的機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的能使用嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它恐怕比OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現有的任何機動戰士都優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這部托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是所有機動戰士的起源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.61,0:13:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部鋼彈\N也是以這機體為出發點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳爸爸的事，我們很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.47,0:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們再早一點知道事態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事請發表一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得非常遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不到這個衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼兇殘的恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞德利安外務次官的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被誘拐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.33,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也正在搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然恐怖份子的目的現在不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.33,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果這是衛星整體的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只好採取軍事行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一等!蕾蒂‧安特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失陪\N我要去搜索恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.78,0:14:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我們說為恐怖份子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們獨斷獨行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.78,0:14:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不把我爸爸送去醫院他會死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為醫院…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳做甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那班人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是OZ的人殺死我爸爸的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別胡來!逃出來已盡了力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳會沒命啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死掉也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺死妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和這個人有何仇怨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別介意，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，我想見希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好機會!   請放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的希洛是希洛‧唯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.41,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識希洛‧唯嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.52,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安演技仍然那麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德利安外務次官呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被殺死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.13,0:15:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心嗎?傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.50,0:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請打開心扉，你有太多秘密了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令!探測到巨大熱源反應!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防衛的里歐被消滅了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會是鋼彈吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫準備好的機動戰士出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視野很差，甚麼也不能確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.17,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就叫我做J博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一名科學家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你派希洛去地球的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，德利安的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.65,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和希洛讀同一間學校真令我嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.62,0:17:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們的發言人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發言人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛擁有高超的判斷能力和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各種戰鬥技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被培育為殺人專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何要那樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.57,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了殖民衛星的和平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.38,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自相殘殺應該不會帶來和平!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭由人發起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能由人完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.35,0:17:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫希洛襲擊的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.49,0:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想發起戰爭...像惡魔一樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.33,0:17:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有更和平的解決方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.83,0:18:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年前，我們也那樣深信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們以為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類並非那麼愚蠢的種族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會希望發生戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民衛星的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我們這種技術者\N和勞動者開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.02,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的祖先拼命製造殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然終於能過正常的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已經過了百年以上的歲月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年前，我們全靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有衛星的指導者-希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.84,0:18:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能繼續過著和平的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛‧唯!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.74,0:18:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們衛星居民來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那名字已經成為傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的行動名字也是抄那名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行動名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，和平的日子並不長久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建立和平的指導者會帶來危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛‧唯被那組織暗殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後，衛星間的聯繫斷絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為聯合軍擴張軍力的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.51,0:19:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ是暗殺希洛‧唯以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想在地球圈發起戰爭的主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸臨死前提起過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫我小心OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你叫希洛襲擊的是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要阻止他們侵佔統一聯合軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.26,0:19:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及在地球圈完全獨裁的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何要把那任務交給希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何一定要他那樣做!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法，因為他明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.01,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們衛星居民心底的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目標看來一致啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼?回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標鎖定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你終究要決一勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.52,0:20:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡能把小姐妳平安送回地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們為何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.50,0:20:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是德利安的…女兒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為小姐妳和希洛有相同的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純真而善良的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他其實是個善良的好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒人能阻止希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.82,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話就不要接近他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.29,0:21:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人情我已還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!戲弄我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.34,0:22:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，我永遠是德利安的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.10,0:22:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.10,0:22:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.60,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.10,0:23:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.60,0:23:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.10,0:23:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.49,0:23:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.86,0:23:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜被拋進轉變的命運裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.77,0:23:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到地球後，等待她的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盛大的學園節以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.57,0:23:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛的轉校通知
